reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Quality product that cleans well with a fabulous smell!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars BEST smelling baby soap!!!!
reviews.reviewText: I love love love this noodle and boo laundry soap. I have washed every load of baby clothes with this wash for 8 months, and I love the way the smell stays in the clothing even after the dry cycle is completed! I have started washing our blankets and towels with it as well due to the wonderful scent that remains in everything after using! The only downfall, every time I receive a new bottle it is leaking. The issue isn’t big enough to take away a start because the product is that great!!!If you’re on the fence I’m here to tell you it is so worth it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: So far the scents holds up for days

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Smells soooo good!!
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely love this detergent. It didn’t irritate my 2 year old’s skin at all and she is super sensitive. It actually made my clothes smell good even after wash & dry. Only complaint is it did come leaking a little in the package. I bought this directly from the company site after that occurrence and it was not leaking that time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Finally a good for you detergent that smells amazing!!
reviews.reviewText: I love the smell. It’s expensive but so well worth it. It’s gentle on your clothes but cleans them very well!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Smells Great, Stains Gone
reviews.reviewText: I have a skin allergy and have been using Dreft. I saw this advertised and thought I'd try it.When the product arrived, even though the tops were covered in plastic wrap, the box was a sticky gooey mess from product leakage. I note other reviews have this problem as well.If you could fix the leakage, I'd rate you a strong 5 stars!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Maybe you don’t need this for everyday laundry but when they’re little it makes the baby smell that much better! It’s the perfect light baby scent

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024

reviews.reviewText: I normally don't like lavender but this has such a light, sweet fragrance, I don't mind it. It is a small bottle and it feels quite pricey, however I only need a small amount per load ( even smaller than concentrated detergent).
I love the detergent- but...not happy that every bottle spilled into the box and became a sticky mess.
I am in love with the smell. So it washes baby cloths very gently. Ovrarll I love this and 100% recommended for newborn baby cloth washing. Will buy again.
